frus:attachment.p:
Having considered the General Assembly resolution
of the 2nd December, 1950 (document A/1616) on the subject of the Ewe
problem;

Noting that certain groups in the two Trust
Territories declined to take part either in certain stages of the elections
or in the proceedings of the enlarged Consultative Commission;

Notes with approval the steps which the Administering
Authorities propose to take in order to encourage these groups to take part
hereafter in the work of the Commission;

Urges these groups to take advantage of these
proposals and to take part accordingly in the second session of the
Commission;
